data.description: Welcome to riverfront living at its finest, where the beauty of nature meets the comfort of home! Nestled at the confluence of three rivers, this stunning property offers breathtaking views from multiple spacious decks. Enjoy the convenience of your private boat dock, perfect for water enthusiasts.  Step inside to discover a newer renovated kitchen and bathroom, complete with stainless steel appliances and modern finishes. Stay comfortable year-round with newer central air, while the partially finished basement offers additional space for your needs.  This home boasts hardwood floors, an outbuilding for extra storage, and a cozy pellet stove for those chilly evenings. The bonus room in the basement could easily serve as a third bedroom or a versatile space for your lifestyle. Did we mention there is a newly renovated 3rd bathroom?  Don't miss out on this rare find - schedule your showing today and experience the tranquility of riverfront living!
